Parameter to control which run periods selectionsare valid for.  
Look at AnalysisUtils.cxx to find run period numbering - Run period 8 = run 5 anti-neutrino data/MC
List valid runs using a comma separated string

 < psycheSteering.Selections.UpgradeNumuCC.ValidRunPeriods           = 23 >
 < psycheSteering.Selections.TrackerNumuCC.ValidRunPeriods           = 0,1,2,3,4,5,6,17,18 >
