-------------------------------------------------------------

Controls whether to include flux as psyche systematic
For the moment in psycheSteering flux syst is treated independetly of the 
rest of the weights as a special flux syst
If the first param is on and the second is off the systematic will return
the normal flux weights as corrections
 < psycheSteering.Systematics.Flux.EnableFlux = 0 > // this is to enable flux syst
 < psycheSteering.Systematics.Flux.Throws = 0 > // this is to do the throws

